Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長身先士卒最先到可真有幹勁哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說緊張得睡不著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向早起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  習慣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還沒習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以…以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿之後六天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的事都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}いまを抜けだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:08.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}手に触れた　Glossy future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}熱くなれることが見つかった時は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}迷わないで　止まらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}素直になっちゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:34.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}荷物かかえ何処にしまえるかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:38.72,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}気にしないの　手ぶらでHurry Hurry！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.63,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}謎はパラレル　意味深パズル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:50.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}負けないから　負けないよと咲う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}楽しくなれたら勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}よしっ！　my mine Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:01.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}広がる心の景色で会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}君は自由に　Fighting start！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}悲しみを抜けだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:12.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}触れた手を握りかえしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:18.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}道の先は明日に続くのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:26.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}考えるより一緒に走ってみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}現在就想要脫出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:08.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}手所觸碰到的是　Glossy future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}當看到能讓人熱血沸騰的事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不要猶豫　不要停下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:28.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}就率直一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:34.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即使是需要把東西收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:38.72,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}也可以毫不在意的　空著手快快趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.63,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}謎題是平行而且具有深意的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:50.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}笑著說不會輸的　不會輸的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只要覺得開心就會勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}很好{\ropj}！{\r}　my mine Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:01.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在延展開來的心中景色裡相會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}請你自由地開始戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}逃離那份悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:12.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相碰觸的手再回握住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:18.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}道路的前方會一直通向明天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:26.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}比起考慮還是一起奔跑試試吧
