Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像每年人數都在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲不在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有些遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  她還不習慣人這麼多的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像沒手機之類的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風越女子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有80名部員的強隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隊長福路美穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能洗刷去年團體賽連勝記錄中斷的污名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要提這事多久才肯罷休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年縣預選的優勝學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井上純
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村智紀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國廣一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕透華
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太適應這麼顯眼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯眼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯眼怎麼了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  面對媒體微笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天江不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要辛苦您解說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體賽必定是龍門渕或風越奪冠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了決賽都只打五次半莊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以您專業的眼光來看今天比賽看點在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕高中的天江衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年天江的活躍的確有目共睹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她打牌的方式簡直就像外行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說她只是運氣好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年全國有超過一萬名高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以夏季大賽為目標參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會出現那麼一兩個無法用常理判斷的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年是西東京的宮永照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是鹿兒島的神代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有天江衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年或許也會出現這種「被牌眷顧的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不信運勢流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我也不想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了  我得去採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是最重要的採訪對象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和  去年全國中學生大賽霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加她的長相  被媒體熱捧也是情理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次與她在店裡對局時沒覺得她有多厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在會是如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的加入  初次參賽的清澄高中也備受矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你們能走多遠呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說想在個人賽決一勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走多遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是全國優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…清澄不只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣可真慢哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又把鬧鐘給弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天去她家設了五個鬧鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼下去就有可能因人數不足喪失比賽資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄高中的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她就是…原村和？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  原村和胸部附近無用脂肪應該更多才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到和衣相似的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再出現個像衣那樣的人  那怎麼受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你們好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為要讓須賀君換女裝上場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒制服的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是擔心這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  原村同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是被採訪著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於從採訪中解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了  原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多看起來很強的對手  我真激動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想趕快和她們對局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是進軍全國的第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓足幹勁儘情發揮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿看來是有成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是忍不住想打麻將呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是對局室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對局室只允許比賽的四人進入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能帶手機  裡面也沒信號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部安裝有數架攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在觀戰室裡觀看比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到加油的聲音還真難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我公佈一下登記的出場順序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒  優希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次鋒  真子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中堅  我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副將  和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據合宿的成長和戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這個順序是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各校每次派出一人  每桌四校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開局10萬點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個半莊結束時換下一個選手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點數繼承到下一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五人完成比賽後點數最高的學校獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有名次獎分和首位獎分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是賽到後半  就越可能因為點數差而束手束腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點數為負立刻結束比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}（無精打采）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  先鋒派最強的出戰才是常理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我最強！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你不會計算點數變化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都做了那麼多練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是錯了一半以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是今年的對戰表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共有五十八所學校參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一輪比賽選出十四所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午第二輪加上兩所種子學校選出四所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這剩下的四所學校在明天進行決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比初中的時候還要多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過和激戰區的大都市圈比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不及人家三分之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一輪的對手好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄  東福寺  千曲東
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定輕鬆取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有個叫原村什麼的  還是初次參賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剛才看到她對記者說要獲得全國優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為胸部大點受到追捧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  第一輪比賽加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一輪比賽馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:09.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各校的先鋒選手請到指定的對局室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到主角的登場時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們在觀戰室給你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦  優希
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（對局室E）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:55.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}縣預選團體賽  第一輪比賽  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:03.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}縣預選團體賽  第一輪比賽  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於揭開戰幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開局由清澄高中的片岡優希坐莊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟上我這人稱最快出牌者的速度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她做成雙東風了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄一上來就鳴牌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙東風加寶牌2  莊家滿貫確定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能棄和扔安全牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊家跳滿  18000點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就是莊家跳滿和大牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄高中  開頭開得很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還行吧  比賽才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人2100點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和  8300點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}清澄的猛攻真是驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希那傢伙越打越來勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就是我也很難阻止她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰快來阻止她啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該放手一搏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一發自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直  斷幺  平胡三色三同順寶牌1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人8300點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真同情她的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的佈陣很有效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這狀態  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和  斷幺一番
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅能量耗盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}E桌先鋒戰  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了回頭來看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也只有在東場厲害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了  被她開始的氣勢震住了最後也只贏了些小牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被她玩弄於股掌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  如果其它學校按原則把強手放在先鋒位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經很頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要防守  把差距拉大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染谷學姐  看似兇險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為真子打了幾年麻將了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都有不上牌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定勝負的牌來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16000點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和  3900點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸  閒家3000點  莊家6000點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}E桌次鋒戰  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬上進行的是E桌中堅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}出場選手請到對局室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和跟咲到二樓咖啡廳吃點什麼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:17:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時攝入香蕉和乳製品  能增強大腦的活躍度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是從電視上的雜學節目看來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給部長加油這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是剛才清澄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透華這傢伙  在哪裡閒逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍門渕高中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是原村和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是原村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確…這胸部正如透華所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過我覺得並非毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透華怎麼會在意這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說這種人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  剛才擦肩而過時不安的感覺消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}E桌中堅戰  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長好像比完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到原村同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個短髮的孩子  到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才感覺到的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是原村和登場哦  去看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和的話  我看過她中學比賽稱霸時的牌譜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術流打法失誤太多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我覺得她很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是透華對她意外地關注
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和可能是「小和和」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得她這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小和和」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是線上麻將界被稱為傳說的那個「小和和」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小和和」是不會失誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟原村和完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小和和」比奇怪的職業選手還要厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果存在那樣的高中生的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就棘手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那樣  我們五人也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是衣和透華現在都不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全和的小牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速攻也和了六回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  和了六回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:02.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬上進行的是E桌副將戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}出場選手請到對局室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要比我更快結束戰鬥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  小和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村出場了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？人好像多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然擁擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是衝著和來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預先佔個座果然明智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（千樣應援團：小野你管家還沒當夠嗎喂）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  萩義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是龍門渕透華
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的變裝也很完美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  原村和呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年全國中學生大賽霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人氣是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不允許有人比我還耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的實力究竟如何  讓我拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到備受矚目的原村登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  小和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:12.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,がんばっちゃった　がんばった我々
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:15.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}東南西北　わーいわーい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:20.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集まれ！わんだーげーむ始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:25.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（はいっ牌　つー牌　はいっ牌　一向聴！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:30.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}（はいっ牌　つー牌　はいっ　多面聴！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:33.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当に悔しければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:36.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣くだけなんてムダです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:40.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こころは次の場所へ走り出したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（挽回逆転）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来{\redc}·{\r}未来は（来来対面）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:47.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来{\redc}·{\r}真っ白（来来混一色）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}{\be1}自分次第ね（ダブ東ドラドラ流して）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃっかり上がろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:57.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やる気だキミ　強気でキミ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楽しくなるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:05.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝ち負けよりも（もーいっかい）　駆け引きさせて（もーいっかい）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その気のキミ　陽気なキミ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.63,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日はもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:16.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一万点　十万点　百万点の世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,がんばっちゃった　がんばった我々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:21.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}聴牌即立直　わーいわーい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:27.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}集まって！わんだーげーむ続けましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}続けましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:12.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧　努力的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:15.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}東南西北　喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:20.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合！讓我們開始這歡樂遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:25.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（配牌　字牌　配牌　一向聽！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:30.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}（配牌　字牌　好啊　多面聽！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:33.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:36.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使哭泣也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:40.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈向著下一個地方飛奔而去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（逆轉挽回）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來·未來就是（來來對面）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:47.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來·一片白色（來來混一色）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}{\be1}還是取決於自己（拿著雙東風兩張寶牌沒和到還下莊了）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見好就收不打了{\redj}？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:57.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿幹勁的你　不服輸的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:05.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起輸贏（再來一次）　還是來用戰略吧（再來一次）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心的你　充滿活力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:16.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著一萬點　十萬點　百萬點的世界前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧　努力的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:21.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}一聽牌就立直　喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:27.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}大家集合！讓我們繼續這歡樂的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}{\be1}讓我們繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:53.11,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1\pos(180,45)}下 回 預 告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:53.11,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1\pos(550,295)}『傳 統』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學  剛才就看你手一直停在牌山上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做實驗
